metadata.title: EcoBorder 4 ft. Black Rubber Landscape Edging (6-Count) (Pack of 2)
description: Give your outdoors a professional appearance with the Eco border Landscape Edging in Black. They're made of sturdy and flexible eco-friendly, 100 percent recycled rubber tires. They won't crack even under extreme weather conditions and are reusable from one season to the next. The border edgings are also non-toxic making them safe for use around children, therefore ideal for playgrounds and sandboxes. Plus, they feature an innovative mower edge design that eliminates the need for the trimmer allowing for a quick, easy installation. The Eco border Landscape Edgings in Black are available in a convenient 6-count package along with the necessary hardware.
